Package net.minestom.server.entity.damage

Class DamageType

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minestom.server.entity.damage.DamageType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataContainer
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EntityDamage, EntityProjectileDamage
    public class DamageType
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataContainer
    Represents a type of damage, required when calling LivingEntity.damage(DamageType, float) and retrieved in EntityDamageEvent.

    This class can be extended if you need to include custom fields and/or methods. Be aware that this class implements DataContainer so you can add your own data to an already existing damage type without any wrapper.
